{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme","result":{"pageContext":{"id":569,"date":"2021-03-18T18:25:51","date_gmt":"2021-03-18T18:25:51","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=569"},"modified":"2023-08-27T06:15:35","modified_gmt":"2023-08-27T06:15:35","slug":"how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-change-the-header-logo-on-your-shopify-theme/","title":{"rendered":"How to change the header logo on your Shopify theme"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"How to change your Shopify theme logo (and make it look good)\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iruCM36n-lA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All Shopify&#8217;s free and premium themes come with a built-in option to change your header&#8217;s logo via the Customize page. This is how you can do it:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-finding-the-customize-page\">Finding the customize page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Customize</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>On the left sidebar, click on <strong>header</strong>. Typically this is the very first option.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"453\" class=\"wp-image-3191\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/aa1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/aa1.jpg 820w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/aa1-768x424.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Search for an option called <strong>Logo Image</strong> or just <strong>logo</strong>. This name may vary from theme to theme, so does its position. Make sure you scroll through all the options to ensure you locate the correct one. <br><br>On most Shopify&#8217;s official free themes, it can be found under the <strong>Theme Settings</strong> field.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"879\" height=\"781\" class=\"wp-image-3189\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/i1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/i1.jpg 879w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/i1-850x755.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/i1-768x682.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 879px) 100vw, 879px\" /><br><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click on <strong>select image</strong> to choose the logo.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click on <strong>save </strong>at the top right corner and that is it! You can now preview your website to ensure it&#8217;s showing up correctly.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UKO9ViFXaWQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">&amp;lt;br>&amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial&#8221; target=&#8221;_blank&#8221; rel=&#8221;noreferrer noopener&#8221;>- Add a collection tabs slider to any store (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)&amp;lt;/a>&amp;lt;iframe width=&#8221;560&#8243; height=&#8221;315&#8243; src=&#8221;https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc&#8221; title=&#8221;YouTube video player&#8221; frameborder=&#8221;0&#8243; allow=&#8221;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&#8221; allowfullscreen=&#8221;&#8221;>&amp;amp;amp;lt;br>&amp;amp;amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps&#8221;>- Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security&amp;amp;amp;lt;/a></iframe><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; How to add a collection with tabs section to any theme (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\"><br><br></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Change or update your theme&#8217;s logo. Works with any Shopify theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":584,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{